node.text:
In some ways it feels like my career went on for a lifetime and in other ways, it flew by like the blink of an eye. This video gave me chills and brought back memories of hard times and lots of memories of good times. Thank you to @crossfitgames and @mariah.moore for this amazing tribute. Cheers to more good times. #HWPO #FRA5ER
-
#HardWorkPaysOff

node.text:
My HWPO Training program is a culmination of years at the elite level of CrossFit and thousands of hours spent refining training methods. #HWPO #FRA5ER
-
My training has always used percentages, scaling, and modifying to make workouts flexible while setting a clear path to elite performance. 
-
The HWPO Training program is not a bunch of random movements crammed together just to spike your heart rate. These workouts are thoughtfully designed to lay down a solid foundation of strength and work capacity.
-
For more information click the link in bio “HWPO Training Program Pre-Sale” or visit Hybridperformancemethod.com/hwpo

node.text:
Mark your calendars, the @fittestfreakest challenge starts November 30th and this year, it’s going digital! #HWPO @niketraining #freakestchallenge 
-
The team elimination challenge kicks off on November 30th and this year, they’ve added an adaptive category. Athletes from anywhere in Europe are welcome to participate in the online qualifier, but only 4 from each division will make it to the final (currently scheduled for the beginning of February 2021). 
-
Due to global restrictions, be sure to check the event page for possible date changes and updates (link in stories).
